Ranger Help for: skin animal
=============================

SYNTAX:      skin <corpse>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   3
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to skin the corpse of a slain creature,
obtaining meat and hide in the process. The hide can be fashioned into
a leather pouch, and leftover meat can be eaten for sustenance. The
size of the pouch depends on how large the corpse was. The Ranger must
be wielding a slash type weapon to perform the skinning. How much
usable material the Ranger gets depends on skill and dexterity.
